<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 12:12:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>34 岁的利多尔·利维 (Lidor Levy) 在以色列南部恐怖袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/lidor-levy-34-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-a8d1-d40c-adef-fff36d4d0000</link><description>利维是周日甘亚夫内购物中心持刀袭击事件中受伤的三人之一，留下了怀孕的妻子、六个月大的婴儿、父母和两个兄弟姐妹</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:42:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/lidor-levy-34-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-a8d1-d40c-adef-fff36d4d0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其航空将所有往返以色列的航班冻结期限延长至 2025 年 3 月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/turkish-airlines-extends-freeze-on-all-flights-to-and-from-israel-until-march-2025/0000018e-a8b2-d801-abce-adf743130000</link><description>国有土耳其航空公司将其特拉维夫航班暂停期延长六个月之际，正值以色列和土耳其之间的外交紧张局势加剧，并且即将迎来以色列最繁忙的旅行季节</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:33:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/turkish-airlines-extends-freeze-on-all-flights-to-and-from-israel-until-march-2025/0000018e-a8b2-d801-abce-adf743130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列抗议者阻挡警察水枪：“我这样做是为了保护人质的家人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protester-who-blocked-police-water-canon-i-did-it-to-protect-hostages-families/0000018e-a889-dfed-ad9f-aadbbb110000</link><description>阿隆·格罗佐夫在耶路撒冷总理内塔尼亚胡官邸外举行抗议活动时，爬到警察高压水枪下，获释后对《国土报》表示：“我想到人质遭到虐待，这就是我坚持下去的动力。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protester-who-blocked-police-water-canon-i-did-it-to-protect-hostages-families/0000018e-a889-dfed-ad9f-aadbbb110000</guid></item><item><title>“我们很遗憾来到这里”：耶路撒冷帐篷营地反内塔尼亚胡抗议的真正含义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-sad-to-be-here-what-the-jerusalem-tent-camp-anti-netanyahu-protest-really-was/0000018e-a486-dd6b-abae-f7c743c30000</link><description>在与警察发生冲突的一个晚上，为期四天的集中营引起人们对加沙人质的关注成为头条新闻，但大多数时候，这是一个由活动人士组成的即时社区，询问如何不屈服于绝望</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-sad-to-be-here-what-the-jerusalem-tent-camp-anti-netanyahu-protest-really-was/0000018e-a486-dd6b-abae-f7c743c30000</guid></item><item><title>即使在以色列袭击大马士革之后，伊朗影子战争的游戏规则也没有改变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/rules-of-the-game-in-iranian-shadow-war-are-unchanged-even-after-israels-damascus-attack/0000018e-a840-dd6b-abae-ff431a9e0000</link><description>周一以色列直接袭击伊朗驻大马士革领事馆后，关键问题是伊朗是否会冒着失去与以色列直接对抗的“抵抗轴心”战略的风险，是否会开辟一条针对以色列的直接战线</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:05:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/rules-of-the-game-in-iranian-shadow-war-are-unchanged-even-after-israels-damascus-attack/0000018e-a840-dd6b-abae-ff431a9e0000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心伊朗威胁，以色列将 GPS 干扰范围扩大到特拉维夫和耶路撒冷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-extends-gps-jamming-to-tel-aviv-and-jerusalem-amid-fears-over-iranian-threats/0000018e-a7dd-dd6b-abae-f7dfc9f20000</link><description>由于担心伊朗对大马士革高级将军遇刺事件做出反应，以色列扩大了 GPS 干扰力度，导致以色列地图服务显示以色列人在贝鲁特和开罗的位置</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 10:17:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-extends-gps-jamming-to-tel-aviv-and-jerusalem-amid-fears-over-iranian-threats/0000018e-a7dd-dd6b-abae-f7dfc9f20000</guid></item><item><title>阿尔及利亚犹太钢琴家莫里斯·埃尔·梅迪奥尼的去世结束了一个音乐时代</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/death-of-algerian-jewish-pianist-maurice-el-medioni-ends-a-musical-era/0000018e-a82f-dd6b-abae-ff6fd5050000</link><description>这位音乐家于上个月去世，享年 95 岁，他将北非音乐与拉丁和非裔美国音乐结合在一起。他在晚年才成名，但在以色列为获得认可而奋斗</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 09:49:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/death-of-algerian-jewish-pianist-maurice-el-medioni-ends-a-musical-era/0000018e-a82f-dd6b-abae-ff6fd5050000</guid></item><item><title>财政部发现，目前现役以色列预备役军人数量是预算的两倍</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/number-of-active-israeli-reservists-currently-double-what-was-budgeted-for-treasury-finds/0000018e-9f75-d6b5-a39f-bf7da0510000</link><description>数千名原本在义务服役后被释放的以色列义务兵在 10 月 7 日之后立即转为预备役军人，并获得了加薪。 IDF：数字比预测高出近 30-40%</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 07:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/number-of-active-israeli-reservists-currently-double-what-was-budgeted-for-treasury-finds/0000018e-9f75-d6b5-a39f-bf7da0510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人权组织向高等法院请愿，迫使政府增加对加沙的援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-human-rights-groups-petition-high-court-to-force-government-to-increase-gaza-aid/0000018e-a41d-d40c-adef-f7ff95e30000</link><description>请愿书由四个人权组织提交，呼吁以色列当局允许所有援助物资、设备和人道主义人员自由、快速和不受阻碍地通行，特别是前往加沙地带北部。政府否认了所有针对它的指控</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 03:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-human-rights-groups-petition-high-court-to-force-government-to-increase-gaza-aid/0000018e-a41d-d40c-adef-f7ff95e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于高度戒备状态，担心伊朗会对大马士革的杀戮进行报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-on-high-alert-amid-fears-iran-will-seek-revenge-for-damascus-killings/0000018e-a595-dfed-ad9f-afdfedbd0000</link><description>所有迹象都表明，德黑兰决心对以色列暗杀叙利亚革命卫队高级指挥官的指控做出回应，而以色列国防军已经加强了防空司令部，以应对可能来自伊斯兰共和国的导弹或无人机袭击。加沙的车队是更广泛现象的征兆：当平民在附近时，士兵们就会开枪。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-on-high-alert-amid-fears-iran-will-seek-revenge-for-damascus-killings/0000018e-a595-dfed-ad9f-afdfedbd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列被拘留加沙人野战医院的医生：“我们都是违法行为的同谋”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/doctor-at-idf-field-hospital-for-detained-gazans-we-are-all-complicit-in-breaking-law/0000018e-a59c-dfed-ad9f-afdfb5ce0000</link><description>以色列监狱设施的一名医生说，“两名囚犯因手铐受伤而被截肢”，他在给部长、总检察长的信中描述了恶劣的条件以及违反医疗道德和法律的行为</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/doctor-at-idf-field-hospital-for-detained-gazans-we-are-all-complicit-in-breaking-law/0000018e-a59c-dfed-ad9f-afdfb5ce0000</guid></item><item><title>600名英国律师呼吁英国停止向以色列出口武器；周日袭击中受伤的男子不治身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article-live/idf-says-it-will-draft-more-reservists-into-air-defense-command-amid-iran-threats/0000018e-a6d1-dfed-ad9f-aedbfc6c0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，将在伊朗威胁下征召更多预备役人员加入防空司令部 ■ 以色列中部增加 GPS 干扰，以阻止无人机威胁 ■ 美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀对援助人员的死亡感到“愤怒” ■ 以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩南部真主党目标 ■ 哈马斯领导人哈尼亚表示，如果以色列国防军不从加沙撤军，就不会达成协议，“光荣的囚犯交换”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 02:03:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article-live/idf-says-it-will-draft-more-reservists-into-air-defense-command-amid-iran-threats/0000018e-a6d1-dfed-ad9f-aedbfc6c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列主要政治民意调查专家去世，享年 78 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-leading-political-pollster-dies-at-78/0000018e-a5db-dd6b-abae-f7db285f0000</link><description>卡米尔·福克斯是 Dialog 民意调查研究所的首席研究员，为媒体提供民意调查和选举样本。他在 2018 年表示，“如果你有求知欲，这就是世界上最有趣的工作”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 21:38:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-leading-political-pollster-dies-at-78/0000018e-a5db-dd6b-abae-f7db285f0000</guid></item><item><title>外国外交官表示，加沙援助人员被杀损害了粮食分配和对以色列国防军的信任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/foreign-diplomats-say-killing-of-aid-workers-in-gaza-harms-food-distribution-trust-in-idf/0000018e-a56b-d24a-abbf-ef6ba2550000</link><description>一名外交官表示，“由于操作故障，向北迁移的援助人员受到了武装分子的威胁，现在显然也受到了以色列国防军的威胁”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 20:07:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/foreign-diplomats-say-killing-of-aid-workers-in-gaza-harms-food-distribution-trust-in-idf/0000018e-a56b-d24a-abbf-ef6ba2550000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡家外发生的一起事件抹去了以色列反政府抗议活动的全部焦点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/one-incident-at-the-protest-outside-the-pms-home-erased-both-october-7-and-the-hostages/0000018e-a4f7-d24a-abbf-eefff1020000</link><description>如果类似的示威活动发生在一个独裁政权的国家，以色列人可能会同情抗议者，即使其中一些人采取暴力行动。 ■ 如果内塔尼亚胡拒绝甘茨9月份举行选举的提议，民族团结党可能会退出政府五月</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 19:38:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/one-incident-at-the-protest-outside-the-pms-home-erased-both-october-7-and-the-hostages/0000018e-a4f7-d24a-abbf-eefff1020000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨提议九月在以色列举行选举；内塔尼亚胡：政府将继续执政直至实现战争目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/gantz-proposes-election-in-september-pm-govt-will-continue-until-war-goals-are-achieved/0000018e-a53b-df61-a1ef-ef7be5b20000</link><description>在周三的新闻发布会上，甘茨表示，他希望“所有负责任的公共领导人都加入联合政府”，随后内塔尼亚胡指责部长在战时处理“小政治”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 19:18:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/gantz-proposes-election-in-september-pm-govt-will-continue-until-war-goals-are-achieved/0000018e-a53b-df61-a1ef-ef7be5b20000</guid></item><item><title>威斯康星州的亲巴勒斯坦抗议投票对拜登来说是坏消息吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-03/ty-article/.highlight/was-wisconsins-pro-palestinian-protest-vote-bad-news-for-biden/0000018e-a4ea-dfed-ad9f-aefbf8130000</link><description>虽然威斯康星州并没有证明对拜登竞选来说是最糟糕的情况，但其他初选州（尽管不是摇摆州）的进步选民表达了他们对白宫针对加沙战争的以色列政策的不满</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-03/ty-article/.highlight/was-wisconsins-pro-palestinian-protest-vote-bad-news-for-biden/0000018e-a4ea-dfed-ad9f-aefbf8130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为杀害援助人员而付出政治代价——当他们不是巴勒斯坦人时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-pays-a-political-price-for-killing-aid-workers-when-theyre-not-palestinians/0000018e-a43f-d24a-abbf-ee3f93d20000</link><description>造成世界中央厨房七名志愿者死亡的袭击是以色列对加沙人道主义援助系统的最新袭击。这次死者大多是西方人，以色列的打击行动将很难</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-pays-a-political-price-for-killing-aid-workers-when-theyre-not-palestinians/0000018e-a43f-d24a-abbf-ee3f93d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列竞争管理局将调查以色列航空公司在加沙战争期间的高票价问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-competition-authority-to-probe-el-al-for-high-airfares-amid-gaza-war/0000018e-a4a7-dd6b-abae-f7e79f1d0000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，大多数外国航空公司暂停飞往以色列的航班，以色列航空的机票价格飙升，主要是飞往美国和欧洲的航班。该航空公司 2023 年第四季度利润同比增长 367%</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 16:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-competition-authority-to-probe-el-al-for-high-airfares-amid-gaza-war/0000018e-a4a7-dd6b-abae-f7e79f1d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 180 天：波兰因涉嫌谋杀而调查援助人员被杀事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-180-poland-to-probe-aid-workers-killing-on-suspicion-of-murder/0000018e-a4bc-dd6b-abae-f7ff675f0001</link><description>波兰表示将调查一名世界中央厨房援助人员因涉嫌谋杀而被杀的事件 ■ 国防部长加兰特：以色列不希望与黎巴嫩发生战争，这“将是一个艰难的挑战” ■ 最新的人质释放/停火提议哈马斯消息人士称，前几轮谈判中止谈判的任何核心问题都没有取得突破 ■ 以下是战争结束 180 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 16:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-180-poland-to-probe-aid-workers-killing-on-suspicion-of-murder/0000018e-a4bc-dd6b-abae-f7ff675f0001</guid></item></channel></rss>